{"tid":884280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【10月31日】中國國家主席被撤銷黨內外一切職務，開除出黨","createTime":"2018-10-31T13:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T11:51:47.000Z","uid":155095,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bb74107dda710da11b5f4176214cefb363513e0d","tid":884280,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:00:30.000Z","msg":"50年前的10月31日，毛澤東主持召開的中共八屆擴大的第十二次全體會議上，批准由江青、康生、謝富治等憑偽證寫成的《<strong>關於叛徒、內奸、工賊劉少奇罪行的審查報告</strong>》，並通過決議：&ldquo;<strong>把時任國家主席劉少奇永遠開除出黨，撤消其黨內外一切職務</strong>&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n維基百科：<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/中国共产党第八届中央委员会第十二次全体会议\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%A7%E5%85%9A%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AB%E5%B1%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E5%A7%94%E5%91%98%E4%BC%9A%E7%AC%AC%E5%8D%81%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1%E5%85%A8%E4%BD%93%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%AE&d=WQC8%2FhqKkWRDHSgIYRUr29tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=e86f4be5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/中国共产党第八届中央委员会第十二次全体会议</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://res.img.ifeng.com/2011/1121/xes_fdd71cdf615ea36f27ce3dcb72447bb2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fres.img.ifeng.com%2F2011%2F1121%2Fxes_fdd71cdf615ea36f27ce3dcb72447bb2.jpg&h=d4e430b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國共產黨第八屆擴大的第十二次中央委員會全會公報<br />\n（一九六八年十月三十一日通過）<br />\n<br />\n 全會批准中央專案審查小組《關於叛徒、內奸、工賊劉少奇罪行的審查報告》。這個報告以充分的證據查明：<br />\n<br />\n黨內頭號走資本主義道路當權派劉少奇，是一個埋藏在黨內的叛徒、內奸、工賊，是罪惡累累的帝國主義、現代修正主義和國民黨反動派的走狗。<br />\n<br />\n全會認為，在無產階級文化大革命中，黨和革命群眾把劉少奇的反革命面貌揭露出來，這是毛澤東思想的一個偉大勝利，這是無產階級文化大革命的一個偉大勝利。<br />\n<br />\n全會對於劉少奇的反革命罪行，表示了極大的革命義憤，一致通過決議：把劉少奇永遠開除出黨，撤消其黨內外的一切職務，並繼續清算劉少奇及其同伙叛黨叛國的罪行。<br />\n<br />\n全會號召全黨同志和全國人民繼續深入展開革命大批判，肅清劉少奇等黨內最大的一小撮走資派的反革命修正主義的思想。<br />\n<br />\n全會公報：<a href=\"http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/64162/64168/64560/65355/4442085.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcpc.people.com.cn%2FGB%2F64162%2F64168%2F64560%2F65355%2F4442085.html&d=WQC8%2FhqKkWRDHSgIYRUr29tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=206e4cd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/64162/64168/64560/65355/4442085.html</a>"},{"pid":"af2b3ba743f7fe8468d15259249b2f284e35dc51","tid":884280,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb04e61501b556c45c296bbecb57ca3ae275d879","tid":884280,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:01:16.000Z","msg":"做乜姐你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3524d0a47050d856cca0e45da340aecc051a2032","tid":884280,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:05:10.000Z","msg":"報左驚先<br />\n好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b61127fe073fc1c6181867c4c66694ff000659d","tid":884280,"uid":30169,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"3524d0a47050d856cca0e45da340aecc051a2032","tid":884280,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:05:10.000Z","msg":"報左驚先<br />\n好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:22:02.000Z","msg":"唔報死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c706fa1a91ad1cd36dea394916ee5493b8bf21","tid":884280,"uid":4575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1b61127fe073fc1c6181867c4c66694ff000659d","tid":884280,"uid":30169,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"3524d0a47050d856cca0e45da340aecc051a2032","tid":884280,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:05:10.000Z","msg":"報左驚先<br />\n好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:22:02.000Z